- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper investigates the impact of language models on automatic speech recognition. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a novel word-based RNN-LM. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with end-to-end ASR systems. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is also possible as the paper deals with processing speech signals.
